=== Space Cruiser Quest ===
{{MessageBox|header=Work in Progress|text=The Space Cruiser Quest is not fully documented. Information is scarce.}}

A separate quest involving locating and defeating a number of Space Cruisers in the NW/outer space regions. Rewards a significant one-time cash bonus (~20 million credits) upon completion. The quest requires finding and capturing an airport/spaceport in the NW.

== SW Arena Masters (Carnutum Ignus Arena) ==

The '''Carnutum Ignus Arena''' (also called the Lava Arena) is Gamma's equivalent of the [[Master Controllers]] in Talsia. It is located in the South West quadrant.

Defeating the SW Arena Masters — a series of escalating Arena fights featuring the [[CyBulwark]] and other champion bots — awards the '''[[Hydroplasmonic Reactor]]''', one of the most powerful reactors available in the game.

Lava Diamonds can also be wagered and multiplied through Arena bets.

