=== Praetorians ===

The Praetorians are the primary enemy faction of Gamma Sector. They are a disciplined, advanced military faction that operates across all four quadrants, guarding meteorite mining operations and ancient Horus temple sites. They are equipped with significantly more powerful tech than the standard Federates of Talsia.

